The paper discusses the integration of RDF and XML data, which is a common topic in database research (cs.DB). The focus on SPARQL and XQuery suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and web technologies (cs.WEB). The use of Linked Data and the Web of Data also suggests a potential overlap with semantic web research (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of update queries suggests a potential overlap with data management (cs.DL).
